WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:24.350 --> 01:26.470
Where did you find these?

01:26.780 --> 01:28.310
I had a dream last night.

01:28.900 --> 01:30.190
Qiao Beiyu told me

01:30.350 --> 01:31.660
there's a music box in the attic.

01:32.420 --> 01:34.310
And I did find it the next day.

01:34.740 --> 01:36.340
Do you think she came to me in my dream

01:37.150 --> 01:39.180
because she had some unfulfilled wish?

01:40.150 --> 01:41.500
What does she want to tell me?

01:41.950 --> 01:42.750
Don't talk nonsense.

01:43.270 --> 01:44.789
What dream?

01:45.340 --> 01:46.539
That's you in the photo, right?

01:47.789 --> 01:48.590
Of course not.

01:48.750 --> 01:49.500
How could it be?

01:50.660 --> 01:51.310
Jinrui.

01:52.310 --> 01:55.509
Lying has consequences.

02:34.460 --> 02:39.360
[Episode 10]
[Never to Be Forgotten]

02:47.500 --> 02:49.190
Move to the right.
More to the right. Down a bit.

02:50.550 --> 02:51.220
Okay.

02:51.750 --> 02:52.550
Haisheng.

02:52.750 --> 02:54.300
The couplet for the doorway is ready.

02:55.550 --> 02:55.780
Here you go.

02:55.780 --> 02:56.220
Slowly now.

02:56.420 --> 02:57.579
Okay. Put it up.

02:58.750 --> 02:59.220
Okay.

03:00.190 --> 03:00.550
Mom.

03:00.830 --> 03:01.830
Here.

03:01.830 --> 03:02.300
Give it to me, Mom.

03:02.390 --> 03:03.470
Come on. Put it up.

03:03.630 --> 03:04.030
All right.

03:05.420 --> 03:06.300
Stick it along the wall edge.

03:07.220 --> 03:08.110
Does it look straight to you?

03:08.300 --> 03:09.390
It's wrong.

03:09.700 --> 03:10.340
This one.

03:10.390 --> 03:10.860
Is it straight?

03:11.110 --> 03:11.910
Yes. That will do.

03:14.060 --> 03:14.860
Stick it evenly.

03:15.390 --> 03:16.470
Looks good.

03:18.700 --> 03:20.110
This one needs to be straight.

03:20.270 --> 03:21.060
Let me see.

03:22.860 --> 03:23.340
How's this?

03:23.470 --> 03:25.579
Move it over a bit.
A little to the right.

03:25.579 --> 03:28.860
[Luck Knocks on The Door]

03:28.860 --> 03:29.670
That's good enough.

03:30.700 --> 03:31.420
All right.

03:32.579 --> 03:33.510
Luck knocks on the door.

03:33.579 --> 03:34.070
All right.

03:35.900 --> 03:37.230
Jinrui is a grown man now.

03:37.550 --> 03:39.350
Why does he still act on a whim?

03:40.020 --> 03:41.420
He was fine during dinner

03:41.550 --> 03:42.390
yesterday.

03:43.180 --> 03:44.180
And then this morning,

03:44.460 --> 03:45.829
he suddenly ran off to Huanzhou.

03:47.550 --> 03:49.070
There were mice in the house yesterday.

03:49.300 --> 03:50.950
Jinrui probably got scared.

03:51.180 --> 03:51.829
Don't be ridiculous.

03:54.230 --> 03:55.670
Today is Xiaoyun's last Chinese New Year

03:55.900 --> 03:57.350
at home before her wedding.

03:57.740 --> 03:58.740
Xiaoyun's parents

03:58.950 --> 04:00.990
asked Jinrui to celebrate with them.

04:01.300 --> 04:02.830
It's understandable.

04:03.900 --> 04:05.550
But going to the bride's home
for the new year?

04:05.550 --> 04:06.550
That is inappropriate.

04:07.350 --> 04:08.270
People might think

04:08.620 --> 04:10.510
Jinrui is being married off
into their family.

04:11.830 --> 04:12.620
Xiaoyun

04:13.350 --> 04:15.420
got her brain scrambled
from too much studying.

04:16.180 --> 04:18.860
Last time she said
they'd only have one child.

04:19.550 --> 04:21.950
If it's a son, fine.

04:22.550 --> 04:23.670
But what if it's a daughter?

04:24.270 --> 04:24.990
What then?

04:25.790 --> 04:27.350
Jinrui is the eldest grandson.

04:27.900 --> 04:30.790
He must ensure
the Qiao family's legacy continues.

04:31.180 --> 04:31.990
Mom.

04:32.950 --> 04:34.110
It's just talk before marriage.

04:34.110 --> 04:35.620
Don't take it seriously.

04:35.860 --> 04:38.620
Once they get married,
Xiaoyun will be part of the Qiao family.

04:38.860 --> 04:41.300
She'll live by our rules.

04:41.900 --> 04:43.180
Fanghao has been through this.

04:44.230 --> 04:45.700
She also said she'd only have one child.

04:46.070 --> 04:48.140
But in the end, she had Qing and Yu.

05:03.140 --> 05:04.070
Where are you running off to now?

05:05.620 --> 05:06.420
I…

05:06.700 --> 05:07.550
I'm getting my phone.

05:09.830 --> 05:10.620
Ma'am.

05:11.580 --> 05:13.140
Why are you still here
during the New Year holidays?

05:14.020 --> 05:14.900
You have my vote

05:14.900 --> 05:15.790
for Employee of the Year next year.

05:16.140 --> 05:16.990
Don't play dumb with me.

05:17.350 --> 05:18.700
Did you see the message I sent you?

05:19.950 --> 05:21.420
I remember now.
My phone ran out of battery.

05:22.620 --> 05:23.790
Yang. Perfect timing.

05:24.020 --> 05:25.700
Assign the new patient to Bed 37.

05:26.020 --> 05:26.460
All right.

05:28.700 --> 05:29.550
Have you thought about

05:29.550 --> 05:30.900
what I mentioned to you?

05:31.110 --> 05:31.990
I'll help Yang.

05:32.700 --> 05:33.180
Ma'am.

05:34.830 --> 05:35.580
Why haven't you gone off duty yet?

05:36.300 --> 05:38.300
Dr. Ming, you came at the right time.

05:38.550 --> 05:39.590
Help me persuade Fang.

05:42.060 --> 05:42.620
What's wrong with her?

05:43.740 --> 05:45.860
I tried setting her up on a blind date.

05:46.260 --> 05:47.260
He's a good guy

05:47.470 --> 05:49.030
from a good family,

05:49.380 --> 05:51.230
but she says she's too busy

05:51.230 --> 05:52.300
and refuses to go.

05:53.030 --> 05:54.150
You know, fate is something

05:54.150 --> 05:55.470
you have to go after yourself.

05:55.790 --> 05:56.620
If you don't even meet the person,

05:56.620 --> 05:58.030
how will you know
if there's a connection?

05:58.260 --> 05:58.860
Dr. Ming,

05:59.060 --> 06:00.380
don't you think I'm making sense?

06:02.860 --> 06:03.380
Yes, you are.

06:09.420 --> 06:09.910
Dr. Ming,

06:10.820 --> 06:13.180
do you really think
I should go on this blind date?

06:15.030 --> 06:16.820
I think you should
give yourself a chance.

06:17.990 --> 06:21.420
You might just meet the right person.

06:21.670 --> 06:22.620
All right. Ma'am.

06:23.350 --> 06:24.940
Let me know when and where.
I'll be there.

06:25.500 --> 06:26.260
Wonderful!

06:26.260 --> 06:27.500
Then it's settled.

06:27.500 --> 06:28.620
Let's go eat.

06:28.910 --> 06:30.300
We'll talk while we eat.

06:31.990 --> 06:32.790
I'm telling you,

06:32.990 --> 06:34.470
you two are a perfect match.

06:35.060 --> 06:36.620
He comes from an excellent background.

06:37.420 --> 06:38.060
And

06:38.060 --> 06:39.180
he's really handsome.

06:40.180 --> 06:41.350
You'll see when you meet him.

06:53.350 --> 06:54.060
Dr. Ming.

06:55.260 --> 06:56.909
Fang didn't pack your food today, right?

06:57.500 --> 06:58.990
You raid my instant noodles again.

07:00.620 --> 07:01.300
My friend.

07:02.590 --> 07:04.030
I missed you,

07:04.420 --> 07:05.380
so I came over to check on you.

07:06.180 --> 07:07.060
That won't fool me.

07:31.110 --> 07:31.590
Yes?

07:31.820 --> 07:32.230
Dr. Ming.

07:33.420 --> 07:35.030
There's a brain injury patient in the ER

07:35.150 --> 07:35.990
with a ruptured liver.

07:36.350 --> 07:37.470
We need you for an emergency consult.

07:38.670 --> 07:40.420
Got it. I'll be right there.

07:47.180 --> 07:48.380
Thanks. I'm off.

08:00.540 --> 08:01.940
[Ming Qiuxin]

08:13.060 --> 08:13.940
Happy New Year!

08:15.990 --> 08:19.390
[Qingyu: Happy New Year!]

08:33.909 --> 08:39.860
[Ming Sheng: What's wrong?]

08:40.350 --> 08:41.980
[Qingyu: Sometimes,
I can't help but feel this way.]

08:41.990 --> 08:46.360
[Me, Qiao Beiyu,
Qiao Jinyu, and Qiao Jinrui.]

08:46.360 --> 08:50.060
[Qingyu: When we succeed,
the adults treat us like treasures,]

08:50.060 --> 08:55.610
[but when we disgrace the family,
they wish we never existed.]

08:56.910 --> 08:59.690
[Ming Sheng: What happened?]

09:02.790 --> 09:04.470
I found the person I was looking for.

09:07.250 --> 09:10.390
[Ming Sheng:
The one who hurt Qiao Beiyu?]

09:10.390 --> 09:11.390
[Qingyu: Yes.]

09:11.390 --> 09:13.860
[Ming Sheng: So, what's your plan now?]

09:14.040 --> 09:15.500
[Qingyu: I don't know.]

09:15.500 --> 09:17.300
If I keep pursuing justice,

09:17.790 --> 09:19.710
I'll have to go against
the entire Qiao family.

09:20.850 --> 09:23.090
[Qingyu: Everyone keeps telling me
to forget about Beiyu]

09:23.090 --> 09:25.690
[and to stop obsessing over
what happened to her.]

09:25.690 --> 09:29.410
[They say that's the right thing to do.]

09:31.790 --> 09:35.850
[Qingyu: Ming Sheng,
if justice and what's right conflict,]

09:36.910 --> 09:38.150
[what would you choose?]

09:45.790 --> 09:47.590
If something isn't just,

09:48.300 --> 09:50.860
how can it even be called right?

10:23.310 --> 10:23.900
It's lit!

10:28.020 --> 10:28.660
Doesn't it look nice?

10:44.950 --> 10:45.470
All right.

10:45.470 --> 10:46.590
Don't the fireworks look amazing?

10:47.130 --> 10:48.740
Jinrui, why did you only buy one?

10:49.130 --> 10:51.090
You only gave me enough money
for one, Mom.

10:52.010 --> 10:52.730
Jinrui,

10:53.290 --> 10:54.930
come with me to buy more.

10:55.170 --> 10:56.050
Okay. Let's go, Grandpa.

10:56.130 --> 10:57.690
Dad, take it slow.

10:58.530 --> 10:59.850
He's acting like a kid again.

10:59.850 --> 11:00.330
Yeah.

11:00.570 --> 11:01.810
We stop it, okay?

11:02.250 --> 11:03.770
No more fireworks. Don't be scared.

11:03.970 --> 11:05.290
Yu, come here.

11:05.290 --> 11:06.610
Come, let me hold you.

11:06.610 --> 11:07.410
Come here.

11:08.930 --> 11:09.890
Good boy.

11:10.490 --> 11:11.410
It's pink.

11:11.690 --> 11:12.530
You were scared just now,

11:12.530 --> 11:13.930
and now you think it's pretty.

11:16.010 --> 11:17.090
Mom, have a mandarin.

11:18.690 --> 11:19.090
This one.

11:19.690 --> 11:20.490
It's cold. Eat it slowly.

11:20.650 --> 11:23.450
Mom, there's something I wanted
to discuss with you.

11:24.410 --> 11:27.370
Fanghao and I have some savings now.

11:27.370 --> 11:29.170
The noodle shop is doing well too.

11:29.770 --> 11:30.730
So, I was thinking

11:31.570 --> 11:33.650
about bringing Bei back with us

11:33.650 --> 11:35.010
to Shunyun.

11:35.650 --> 11:37.930
Why move to Shunyun

11:38.410 --> 11:39.490
when she's living just fine here?

11:41.290 --> 11:43.930
Do you think we're mistreating Bei?

11:44.170 --> 11:44.730
No.

11:44.930 --> 11:47.530
Are you still bothered about us
asking for Bei's living expenses?

11:47.690 --> 11:48.810
No.

11:48.810 --> 11:50.250
We're just worried
that you're too tired.

11:51.250 --> 11:51.770
I'm not tired.

11:52.290 --> 11:54.570
The kids liven things up.

11:54.650 --> 11:57.090
Besides, Bei and Jinrui have been close
since childhood.

11:57.210 --> 11:59.370
They keep each other company,
making things easier for you.

12:00.570 --> 12:01.730
You two are out there

12:01.730 --> 12:03.250
making money to support the family

12:03.850 --> 12:05.290
while raising three kids.

12:05.570 --> 12:06.770
Can you handle it?

12:06.890 --> 12:07.330
We can.

12:07.650 --> 12:09.330
Don't let Yu suffer because of it.

12:10.530 --> 12:12.050
Yanfen, how can you say that?

12:12.330 --> 12:14.570
The three of them are all my children.

12:14.650 --> 12:16.170
I care about each of them equally.

12:16.730 --> 12:18.370
Beiyu is growing up.

12:18.570 --> 12:20.370
I just want to be closer to her.

12:22.490 --> 12:25.850
No matter what, we can't let Yu suffer.

12:26.290 --> 12:27.090
Can you really handle

12:27.290 --> 12:27.970
all three kids?

12:27.970 --> 12:28.930
We can, Mom.

12:37.130 --> 12:37.810
How about this?

12:38.690 --> 12:40.250
Take Bei with you,

12:40.690 --> 12:41.810
but leave Qing here with us.

12:41.970 --> 12:43.530
Qing is still too young.

12:44.490 --> 12:46.330
Keeping her here
will just cause trouble for you.

12:47.410 --> 12:48.930
Why not ask Bei?

12:49.490 --> 12:50.210
Bei,

12:50.410 --> 12:53.130
do you want to go back
with your parents

12:53.330 --> 12:54.410
and leave Qing here?

13:13.780 --> 13:14.590
Come on, say something.

13:14.860 --> 13:16.310
Let Qing stay in your place.

13:23.190 --> 13:24.190
I don't want to go to Shunyun.

13:26.660 --> 13:28.740
See? Such a good girl.

13:28.990 --> 13:29.710
She can stay here

13:29.710 --> 13:31.990
and keep Jinrui company.

13:32.110 --> 13:32.830
That's great.

13:37.780 --> 13:38.860
I have no idea what you were thinking.

13:40.830 --> 13:41.350
Bei.

13:42.470 --> 13:43.230
Have a mandarin.

13:49.470 --> 13:50.110
It's good, isn't it?

13:50.660 --> 13:51.230
Such a good boy.

14:08.190 --> 14:08.660
Ming Sheng,

14:09.540 --> 14:11.140
I know what I need to do now.

14:13.660 --> 14:16.070
In so many moments I didn't notice,

14:17.740 --> 14:20.020
Beiyu was always there,
silently watching over me.

14:22.140 --> 14:22.900
Now,

14:23.780 --> 14:26.310
I want to do the right thing for her.

14:45.050 --> 14:45.860
Ancestors.

14:47.710 --> 14:49.710
Today is the first day
of the Chinese New Year.

14:50.620 --> 14:53.540
I've brought the Qiao family descendants
to pay respects.

14:54.860 --> 14:57.110
We are grateful for your blessings.

15:08.310 --> 15:10.140
You've been part of the Qiao family
for over ten years,

15:11.350 --> 15:12.660
married to me for over ten years,

15:15.430 --> 15:16.710
and we've fought for over ten years.

15:19.110 --> 15:20.990
[Tomb of My Wife Qin Wenqiu]
I treated you well, didn't I?

15:23.990 --> 15:25.230
Yet you got tired of me

15:26.830 --> 15:27.900
and left without a word.

15:34.110 --> 15:34.900
Wenqiu.

15:36.590 --> 15:38.070
You're now resting
in the Qiao family's ancestral grave.

15:45.430 --> 15:47.540
I'm burning this for you. Accept it.

15:49.500 --> 15:51.950
Buy whatever you like.

15:55.950 --> 15:57.430
If we meet again in the next life,

15:58.430 --> 15:59.350
I'll take care of you too.

16:01.310 --> 16:02.540
You like kids.

16:04.430 --> 16:05.780
We'll settle down

16:07.430 --> 16:08.190
and have a child.

16:17.230 --> 16:17.950
I'm leaving now.

16:18.860 --> 16:20.070
I'll visit you again.

16:56.950 --> 16:58.660
Jiangsheng, move that flower pot aside.

16:58.660 --> 17:00.310
Take a good look inside.

17:00.950 --> 17:02.230
We've searched twice already.

17:02.590 --> 17:03.620
A ring that big

17:03.710 --> 17:05.380
wouldn't still be missing
if it were lost at home.

17:06.710 --> 17:08.230
Yanfen,
are you sure it wasn't lost outside?

17:08.230 --> 17:09.140
I didn't even go out.

17:12.589 --> 17:13.780
Where are you going?

17:14.260 --> 17:15.310
Where else?

17:15.310 --> 17:16.950
I'm going back to school
as classes are starting.

17:17.069 --> 17:17.589
Hey.

17:19.109 --> 17:21.380
Your outfit

17:21.740 --> 17:23.109
and bag are new, right?

17:23.349 --> 17:24.589
Where did you get the money to buy them?

17:25.470 --> 17:26.310
Aunt Yanfen.

17:27.500 --> 17:29.140
Are you accusing me

17:29.140 --> 17:30.710
of stealing the gold ring?

17:31.260 --> 17:33.590
I'm not that skilled.

17:33.620 --> 17:35.310
Don't be cheeky with me.

17:36.430 --> 17:39.780
I asked where you got all these from.

17:42.780 --> 17:43.900
Where else?

17:45.190 --> 17:46.310
My boyfriend bought them for me.

17:46.950 --> 17:47.740
Listen to this.

17:47.740 --> 17:49.190
How dare you speak like that!

17:49.350 --> 17:50.660
Calm down, old man.

17:52.740 --> 17:53.430
Found it.

17:56.540 --> 17:57.110
Yanfen.

17:57.260 --> 17:58.190
It's right here.

18:08.110 --> 18:09.020
Aunt Qin.

18:09.020 --> 18:11.020
[Tomb of My Wife Qin Wenqiu]

18:11.020 --> 18:12.860
Thank you for taking care of Qiao Beiyu
all this time.

18:38.950 --> 18:40.630
If you knew about my decision,

18:41.540 --> 18:42.390
would you agree with it?

18:42.820 --> 18:44.740
They chose to sacrifice you

18:45.300 --> 18:46.540
to cover up Jinrui's parentage.

18:47.740 --> 18:49.540
I will make those who hurt you

18:49.870 --> 18:51.020
pay the price.

18:53.190 --> 18:55.670
I'm doing this not just for you

18:56.340 --> 18:57.670
but also for myself.

18:58.670 --> 18:59.870
I want to understand

19:00.670 --> 19:02.630
what kind of world this truly is.

19:20.410 --> 19:21.490
[Sheng]

19:21.860 --> 19:23.410
[Qingyu: Are you there?]

19:26.920 --> 19:31.590
[Qingyu: Ming Sheng, I have got a plan.]

19:31.590 --> 19:35.490
[Ming Sheng: Qiao Qingyu,
do what you want to do.]

19:35.490 --> 19:37.510
[I'll always have your back.]

19:41.560 --> 19:42.460
[Qingyu: Okay.]

19:55.630 --> 19:56.710
Dad, Mom,

19:57.190 --> 19:57.950
we're back.

19:59.390 --> 20:00.100
Xiaoyun's here.

20:00.230 --> 20:00.710
Madam.

20:00.710 --> 20:01.060
Dad.

20:01.780 --> 20:03.020
I missed you so much!

20:03.020 --> 20:04.340
I missed you too, madam.

20:04.710 --> 20:05.870
Still calling her "madam"?

20:06.430 --> 20:08.020
You should start calling her Mom.

20:08.780 --> 20:09.430
Right.

20:09.820 --> 20:10.500
Xiaoyun.

20:10.990 --> 20:12.540
Jinrui said he prepared a gift for me.

20:12.540 --> 20:13.150
Where is it?

20:13.300 --> 20:14.190
Ask him about it.

20:15.060 --> 20:17.020
How rude you are to ask guests for gifts

20:17.020 --> 20:17.630
the moment they arrive.

20:17.630 --> 20:19.540
It's okay, Mom.
I'm not a guest anymore.

20:19.580 --> 20:20.950
From now on, we're family.

20:21.150 --> 20:21.500
Right.

20:22.060 --> 20:22.950
I'll make you some tea.

20:24.100 --> 20:25.260
Xiaoyun, let me help you.

20:25.780 --> 20:26.390
I'll do it.

20:28.390 --> 20:30.990
Xiaoyun, are you staying
in the old house this time?

20:31.430 --> 20:32.740
Jinrui and I talked it over.

20:32.950 --> 20:34.820
We'll stay in his new house first.

20:34.950 --> 20:37.230
We'll move to the old house
when the wedding takes place.

20:37.910 --> 20:39.230
Such a pity.

20:42.300 --> 20:44.020
A lot of guests will be visiting
over the next few days.

20:44.300 --> 20:45.740
Buy some sunflower seeds
and candied fruits

20:45.740 --> 20:46.500
to entertain them.

20:46.870 --> 20:47.950
If there's any leftover,

20:47.950 --> 20:49.390
buy something for yourselves.

20:49.910 --> 20:51.190
You are so generous, Jinrui!

20:53.950 --> 20:54.580
Come on, Qingyu.

20:55.430 --> 20:55.870
Let's go.

20:56.430 --> 20:57.540
Have some tea.

21:01.100 --> 21:02.190
You must be tired after the long trip.

21:02.190 --> 21:02.710
Not at all.

21:02.950 --> 21:03.740
Have a seat.

21:04.780 --> 21:05.910
Jinrui, come here!

21:05.910 --> 21:06.340
Coming.

21:08.630 --> 21:10.470
This one is ten. That one's ten too.

21:10.470 --> 21:11.020
I'll take both.

21:11.020 --> 21:11.710
All right.

21:12.300 --> 21:13.540
Qing, Yu, you're back.

21:13.540 --> 21:14.100
Yes.

21:15.580 --> 21:16.100
All right.

21:18.190 --> 21:19.430
Yu, you're back.

21:25.710 --> 21:27.230
Qingyu, I'm going to buy some pop rocks.

21:32.710 --> 21:34.470
Madam, do you have any pop rocks?

21:46.740 --> 21:47.980
[Notice]

21:47.990 --> 21:49.400
[Closed for the Chinese New Year,]

21:49.400 --> 21:50.760
[reopening after the 15th
of the first lunar month.]

21:57.670 --> 21:58.710
Qingyu, look.

22:02.780 --> 22:03.390
Try some.

22:04.100 --> 22:04.710
No.

22:05.780 --> 22:06.540
Why not?

22:06.540 --> 22:07.780
It's Jinrui's treat.

22:07.820 --> 22:08.540
Might as well enjoy it.

22:09.540 --> 22:09.910
Here.

22:10.990 --> 22:11.710
I don't want it.

22:12.060 --> 22:13.020
Just take it.

22:14.950 --> 22:15.990
I said no.

22:29.230 --> 22:29.950
Thank you.

22:37.870 --> 22:40.100
My mom said music is her dream.

22:40.710 --> 22:42.540
She'll always put music first.

22:43.990 --> 22:45.910
What's your dream?

22:47.020 --> 22:47.630
My dream?

22:49.950 --> 22:51.390
For a long time,

22:51.910 --> 22:53.740
I didn't even know what I wanted.

22:54.540 --> 22:55.780
Like most people,

22:56.470 --> 22:57.820
I just followed
the conventional path forward.

23:00.150 --> 23:02.710
Anna's passion for music taught me

23:03.060 --> 23:04.500
what it means to truly love something.

23:05.670 --> 23:07.020
Before meeting her,

23:07.340 --> 23:08.740
I didn't have a dream.

23:09.630 --> 23:10.780
But after meeting her,

23:11.340 --> 23:12.670
she became my dream.

23:17.870 --> 23:19.390
I'll do anything to help her accomplish

23:19.500 --> 23:21.260
what she wants to achieve.

23:24.540 --> 23:25.630
I'll go help her now.

23:56.500 --> 23:58.260
Mumu, thank you

23:58.260 --> 23:59.710
for coming all this way.

24:00.100 --> 24:02.020
No need for that between us.

24:02.020 --> 24:03.580
Besides, it's urgent.

24:05.500 --> 24:08.260
Qingyu, is everything written here true?

24:09.500 --> 24:10.390
Yes.

24:12.150 --> 24:13.580
Are you sure
you want to go through with this?

24:14.740 --> 24:15.780
Have you thought about

24:15.780 --> 24:16.950
how revealing this

24:17.150 --> 24:18.390
will destroy Qiao Jinrui

24:18.390 --> 24:19.780
and your family?

24:20.470 --> 24:21.540
No matter what happened,

24:21.780 --> 24:22.780
your cousin

24:23.100 --> 24:24.470
is young and promising.

24:25.300 --> 24:26.430
And he's getting married.

24:26.710 --> 24:28.540
His bright future is just beginning.

24:29.610 --> 24:30.770
Your uncle's family,

24:30.990 --> 24:32.390
your grandparents, and your parents.

24:32.500 --> 24:33.950
They definitely don't want the past

24:33.950 --> 24:35.230
to be dredged up again.

24:36.470 --> 24:37.670
But I have to do it.

24:42.230 --> 24:43.390
I've always thought

24:44.150 --> 24:45.870
you and Ming Sheng were alike.

24:46.340 --> 24:48.020
You both hold onto your beliefs

24:48.020 --> 24:48.670
no matter what.

24:50.150 --> 24:50.500
Here.

24:51.390 --> 24:51.820
Take it.

24:52.150 --> 24:52.910
Good luck.

24:54.340 --> 24:54.990
Thank you.

24:55.430 --> 24:56.390
I need to leave now.

24:56.950 --> 24:58.020
Take care on your way back.

25:13.960 --> 25:18.760
[The Sorrow That Shouldn't Be Forgotten]

25:39.870 --> 25:40.500
Um…

25:41.780 --> 25:42.870
Have you decided

25:43.100 --> 25:44.300
how much to put in the red envelope

25:44.390 --> 25:45.580
for Jinrui's wedding tomorrow?

25:46.710 --> 25:47.500
You just remembered?

25:49.100 --> 25:49.820
I've already prepared it.

25:50.910 --> 25:51.390
How much?

25:52.100 --> 25:52.780
Don't worry about it.

25:53.540 --> 25:55.740
Should I go ask Jiangsheng?

25:57.430 --> 25:58.710
Giving too little
wouldn't be appropriate.

26:03.910 --> 26:04.630
How much are you giving him?

26:26.670 --> 26:27.390
Aunt Fanghao.

26:27.870 --> 26:29.060
Can I come in?

26:29.150 --> 26:29.740
Sure.

26:41.870 --> 26:42.500
Jinrui,

26:43.300 --> 26:44.670
you're about to get married.

26:46.630 --> 26:49.630
This is a little something
from your uncle and me.

26:50.710 --> 26:52.230
You must accept it.

26:52.990 --> 26:54.020
Thank you, Aunt Fanghao.

26:58.580 --> 26:59.430
[Passbook]
We've saved quite a bit

26:59.430 --> 27:00.990
over the past two years.

27:02.150 --> 27:03.950
I can't accept this.

27:04.430 --> 27:06.020
This is my way of making amends
to your family.

27:06.100 --> 27:07.470
There's no way I'd take it back.

27:09.910 --> 27:11.340
Jinrui, listen to me.

27:13.260 --> 27:15.470
Back then, when the incident
with you and Beiyu happened,

27:16.230 --> 27:18.820
I only wanted to find you

27:19.540 --> 27:20.500
and ask you face-to-face

27:20.580 --> 27:21.870
what really happened.

27:22.670 --> 27:24.430
When I returned here,
your mother wouldn't let me see you.

27:25.300 --> 27:27.100
I went to your university to find you,
but you avoided me.

27:27.630 --> 27:28.670
At that point,

27:28.870 --> 27:30.300
I more or less understood the situation.

27:31.190 --> 27:32.390
Then, you started working.

27:32.950 --> 27:34.470
One day, you suddenly came to Shunyun,

27:34.780 --> 27:36.630
begging us for forgiveness
no matter what,

27:37.230 --> 27:39.060
and insisting
that we accept this passbook.

27:40.190 --> 27:41.580
I didn't want to take it.

27:41.950 --> 27:43.630
It was your uncle who accepted it.

27:43.630 --> 27:44.630
Do you remember that?

27:45.580 --> 27:46.540
Afterward, he told me

27:47.390 --> 27:48.950
that no matter what,
you were still just a kid

27:49.580 --> 27:51.300
and deserved a chance
to make things right.

27:52.190 --> 27:53.910
He said
we'd keep this money safe for you

27:54.190 --> 27:56.300
and return it
when you needed it in the future.

27:56.670 --> 27:57.820
Now you're getting married,

27:58.020 --> 27:59.230
so it's just the right time for it.

27:59.780 --> 28:00.430
I'll take my leave now.

28:00.430 --> 28:01.540
Aunt Fanghao, this…

28:01.780 --> 28:02.470
Jinrui!

28:02.990 --> 28:04.300
Has my wedding dress arrived?

28:04.670 --> 28:05.780
Aunt Fanghao, you're here too.

28:05.780 --> 28:07.430
Welcome back. I'll leave you two to it.

28:09.300 --> 28:09.990
What was that about?

28:10.670 --> 28:13.020
Nothing.
She just came to congratulate us.

28:15.060 --> 28:15.540
It's here.

28:27.630 --> 28:28.300
Yanfen,

28:28.910 --> 28:31.500
I heard that the secretary will be officiating

28:31.500 --> 28:32.470
Jinrui's wedding. Is that so?

28:32.910 --> 28:35.670
Not just that!
Jinrui's superiors are coming too.

28:35.780 --> 28:37.580
Not everyone gets
that kind of treatment.

28:37.670 --> 28:38.780
Those are big shots!

28:38.780 --> 28:39.780
That's right.

28:40.230 --> 28:42.500
Marrying a city girl
makes all the difference.

28:42.950 --> 28:44.670
We all get to bask in the glory.

28:44.670 --> 28:45.060
Indeed.

28:45.870 --> 28:46.580
Bask in the glory?

28:47.230 --> 28:49.230
If anyone's basking,
it's thanks to Jinrui.

28:49.300 --> 28:50.260
Those officials are coming

28:50.260 --> 28:52.230
out of respect for him.

28:53.340 --> 28:55.020
Grandma,
what's this about basking in glory?

28:55.910 --> 28:56.740
Here you are, Qing.

28:57.190 --> 28:58.670
We were just talking about Jinrui.

28:58.670 --> 28:59.990
The future of the Qiao family

28:59.990 --> 29:01.710
will depend on him.

29:01.950 --> 29:02.820
That's not necessarily true.

29:03.100 --> 29:03.710
Qingyu.

29:05.340 --> 29:06.340
Go upstairs and do your homework.

29:06.630 --> 29:07.300
I already did it.

29:07.910 --> 29:10.630
Then take the box of wedding sweets
to the storage room.

29:16.990 --> 29:17.500
Check these out.

29:17.710 --> 29:19.260
We bought the most expensive sweets.

29:19.390 --> 29:20.670
Yes. We can't even
bring ourselves to eat them.

29:20.910 --> 29:22.580
Do you think one box is enough?

29:24.020 --> 29:24.630
Let me take that.

29:29.580 --> 29:30.260
Thank you.

29:30.780 --> 29:31.390
Qing.

29:40.430 --> 29:42.100
I was young and foolish,

29:42.580 --> 29:43.630
and I hurt Beiyu.

29:44.470 --> 29:45.780
I don't know
if Uncle Lusheng and Aunt Fanghao

29:45.780 --> 29:46.990
ever told you this,

29:47.580 --> 29:49.100
but all these years,
I've been hiding it from my parents,

29:49.100 --> 29:50.630
trying my best
to make amends to your family.

29:52.300 --> 29:54.390
I completely understand
if you blame or resent me.

29:54.670 --> 29:56.230
But we're still family.

29:57.100 --> 29:58.670
And Beiyu can't come back.

29:59.630 --> 30:00.260
Qing,

30:00.820 --> 30:02.580
I just want a chance

30:03.470 --> 30:05.300
to take care of your family
on Beiyu's behalf.

30:07.260 --> 30:08.710
I'll do everything I can
to make it up to you.

30:10.020 --> 30:11.190
Would you accept any consequences

30:11.300 --> 30:12.820
to make amends for Beiyu?

30:13.230 --> 30:13.740
Of course.

30:16.020 --> 30:18.260
Good. After all, we're family.

30:44.020 --> 30:45.150
Everyone else is busy.

30:45.150 --> 30:46.820
Yet, here you are, slacking off.

30:46.990 --> 30:48.870
Well, they couldn't find me.

30:49.710 --> 30:51.820
By the way, Qingyu,
I've noticed something.

30:53.910 --> 30:54.950
Apparently,

30:55.190 --> 30:57.260
no one dares go near this room.

30:58.150 --> 31:00.820
Don't you think they're just too scared?

31:00.990 --> 31:03.340
They won't step foot in here

31:03.430 --> 31:04.470
just because Aunt Qin used to live here.

31:05.060 --> 31:06.300
They're not scared.

31:06.820 --> 31:07.870
They feel guilty.

31:09.540 --> 31:12.540
Yu, you're grown up now.

31:12.780 --> 31:15.060
From now on,
you're the only boy in the family.

31:15.390 --> 31:17.230
You need to take on more responsibility
for Mom and Dad.

31:17.580 --> 31:18.950
They're getting older.

31:19.230 --> 31:21.630
Mom's back and waist are always in pain.

31:21.870 --> 31:23.910
Dad keeps everything bottled up inside.

31:23.950 --> 31:25.260
Wait. Stop right there.

31:25.670 --> 31:27.950
What do you mean by "the only boy"?

31:29.470 --> 31:32.150
Are you dumping everything on me
just because you can't get your name

31:32.150 --> 31:33.230
in the genealogy book?

31:34.190 --> 31:38.060
Being a man is stressful too, you know.

31:38.670 --> 31:41.540
You can have my spot
on the genealogy book.

31:41.870 --> 31:43.950
What kind of twisted logic is that?

31:45.820 --> 31:47.340
Even the smartest person
would go dumb from your beating.

31:53.630 --> 31:55.390
That's the last time I hit you anyway.

32:05.740 --> 32:06.100
Mom.

32:07.740 --> 32:08.020
Here's some tea.

32:08.540 --> 32:09.300
Thank you.

32:09.300 --> 32:09.820
It's hot.

32:09.910 --> 32:10.230
Okay.

32:10.230 --> 32:10.820
Be careful.

32:13.060 --> 32:15.870
You could stay a few more days.

32:16.230 --> 32:18.060
I can show you
around the nearby universities.

32:18.710 --> 32:20.390
Once you see them in person,

32:21.300 --> 32:22.470
you might feel differently.

32:22.470 --> 32:22.990
It's fine.

32:23.780 --> 32:25.230
Besides, I've already booked my flight.

32:27.470 --> 32:29.060
You came just as I'm busy
with my performance.

32:29.430 --> 32:30.580
I don't even have time
to keep you company.

32:31.340 --> 32:32.260
Give me another chance.

32:35.100 --> 32:37.020
Once I enroll in a university here,

32:37.340 --> 32:38.430
we'll have plenty of chances
to see each other.

32:39.300 --> 32:39.990
Besides,

32:40.820 --> 32:42.580
I have something more important to do.

32:43.150 --> 32:44.260
Something more important?

32:44.910 --> 32:45.540
What is it?

32:47.630 --> 32:48.910
It's a secret.

32:50.500 --> 32:51.630
You've got a secret now?

32:53.230 --> 32:54.430
Now you've got me curious.

32:59.870 --> 33:00.340
Fine, I won't pry.

33:01.470 --> 33:03.150
Everyone's entitled to their secrets.

33:06.470 --> 33:06.910
Mom.

33:08.500 --> 33:09.710
All these years have gone by.

33:10.780 --> 33:11.630
I've grown up.

33:13.150 --> 33:13.780
And you…

33:17.710 --> 33:18.470
I have a feeling

33:19.390 --> 33:20.780
that the person most suitable for you

33:21.340 --> 33:22.150
is right by your side.

33:24.780 --> 33:25.670
You're quite the worrier.

33:27.540 --> 33:29.020
Mind your own business, will you?

33:29.740 --> 33:31.870
Fine. I was just saying it anyway.

33:49.870 --> 33:50.470
Mom.

33:51.150 --> 33:52.300
Is your shoulder hurting again?

33:54.060 --> 33:54.870
Let me massage it for you.

33:57.820 --> 33:58.230
I'm fine.

34:01.430 --> 34:02.740
Why aren't you asleep yet?

34:02.740 --> 34:04.430
Jinyu snores. I can't fall asleep.

34:04.820 --> 34:05.500
Where's Dad?

34:05.870 --> 34:07.950
He's probably off drinking

34:07.950 --> 34:08.870
with your uncles.

34:12.429 --> 34:13.500
I'm fine. You don't have to do this.

34:15.190 --> 34:15.580
Mom.

34:16.780 --> 34:18.630
Why did you marry Dad?

34:20.100 --> 34:21.190
Why are you asking this?

34:23.190 --> 34:24.500
Aunt Yanfen said

34:24.500 --> 34:25.949
you didn't want to have so many kids.

34:26.580 --> 34:27.500
If that's the case,

34:27.739 --> 34:29.230
why did you still marry
into the Qiao family?

34:36.190 --> 34:37.340
My parents passed away
when I was young.

34:38.710 --> 34:40.230
I grew up with my grandmother.

34:40.870 --> 34:42.500
When I was young, our family was poor,

34:42.909 --> 34:43.949
and there wasn't any money for school.

34:44.670 --> 34:46.429
So I ended up taking a temping job.

34:50.060 --> 34:51.949
I met your father
at the power supply station

34:51.949 --> 34:52.670
in town.

34:54.670 --> 34:56.429
I was just in my early 20s.

34:58.710 --> 35:00.910
I had to do
all the toughest and nastiest jobs

35:00.910 --> 35:01.870
in the cafeteria.

35:03.230 --> 35:06.500
Your dad couldn't stand to see it,
so he came to help.

35:09.580 --> 35:10.950
One day, he came to me

35:11.430 --> 35:14.990
and said he was a regular employee

35:15.910 --> 35:17.150
with a good salary and benefits.

35:18.740 --> 35:20.340
If we get married,
we can even get a house.

35:23.540 --> 35:25.470
And then we ended up getting married.

35:30.060 --> 35:34.500
Then, your grandparents
wanted grandchildren.

35:35.270 --> 35:36.830
Then we had Jinyu.

35:38.910 --> 35:39.620
But

35:41.500 --> 35:43.140
who would've thought
your father's job would…?

35:44.990 --> 35:46.390
Do you regret it?

35:47.390 --> 35:48.700
What's the use of regretting?

35:50.350 --> 35:52.140
Life still goes on.

35:54.430 --> 35:55.140
Qingyu.

35:56.540 --> 35:57.870
I know you've always struggled

35:59.470 --> 36:01.100
with what happened to your sister.

36:03.180 --> 36:06.430
But sometimes,
you have to let things go.

36:06.910 --> 36:09.430
Things aren't always clear-cut.

36:12.700 --> 36:13.620
Give it time.

36:15.310 --> 36:19.390
It'll smooth itself out.

36:23.500 --> 36:24.390
Got it.

36:32.100 --> 36:33.470
Let me massage your shoulder
a little more.

36:35.580 --> 36:36.390
I'm fine.

36:37.870 --> 36:38.540
You don't need to do this.

37:21.990 --> 37:23.840
[The Sorrow That Shouldn't Be Forgotten]

39:09.360 --> 39:14.480
[Ming Sheng: After tomorrow,
everyone will know about everything.]

39:14.480 --> 39:16.510
[Are you afraid?]

39:17.510 --> 39:21.460
[Qingyu: I'm not.]

40:01.990 --> 40:05.140
[Wedding of Qiao Jinrui and Nie Xiaoyun]

40:09.310 --> 40:10.990
Qiao, look who's here.

40:11.020 --> 40:11.500
Haisheng.

40:12.310 --> 40:13.020
Congratulations!

40:13.220 --> 40:15.390
Come in! Join the celebration!

40:16.350 --> 40:17.020
It's a blessed day.

40:17.020 --> 40:17.750
Congratulations.

40:17.750 --> 40:18.270
It's a joyful day.

40:18.540 --> 40:19.310
Sir,

40:19.750 --> 40:21.620
having you officiate the wedding today

40:21.660 --> 40:23.180
is truly a blessing for the couple.

40:23.620 --> 40:24.700
It's my duty.

40:24.910 --> 40:25.910
Jinrui

40:25.990 --> 40:27.990
is the pride of Nanqiao Village.

40:29.500 --> 40:30.870
Jinrui is so filial.

40:31.020 --> 40:32.500
He insisted on having the banquet here
in the village.

40:33.060 --> 40:34.790
Everyone here watched him grow up.

40:34.950 --> 40:36.020
Of course, he would invite

40:36.020 --> 40:38.270
all his elders to celebrate his big day!

40:39.060 --> 40:41.910
Jinrui has been ahead in everything
since he was a kid.

40:41.910 --> 40:43.620
Studies, work,

40:43.990 --> 40:46.100
and now even marriage!

40:46.790 --> 40:47.990
Marriage this year,

40:48.060 --> 40:51.470
a healthy baby boy next!

40:51.540 --> 40:52.790
That would be wonderful!

40:53.100 --> 40:55.390
Not just one. A boy and a girl.

40:56.350 --> 40:58.660
I'll take your word for it.
Double the blessings!

41:00.910 --> 41:01.700
Come in, please.

41:01.950 --> 41:02.620
Old friend!

41:02.660 --> 41:03.790
Sir.

41:03.790 --> 41:04.580
Congratulations!

41:07.010 --> 41:08.410
The makeup needs a quick fix.

41:08.490 --> 41:09.620
The ceremony is about to start.

41:10.490 --> 41:11.850
I do bridal makeup every day,

41:12.050 --> 41:13.890
but it's my first time
seeing such a beautiful bride

41:14.010 --> 41:15.330
with such fair skin!

41:15.970 --> 41:16.910
You'll surely be

41:17.170 --> 41:18.750
the most beautiful of all in Shunyun
at the wedding.

41:19.170 --> 41:20.470
Xiaoyun is from Huanzhou.

41:20.730 --> 41:21.910
She's a Huanzhou beauty born and bred.

41:22.770 --> 41:24.290
Women in a small county like Shunyun

41:24.290 --> 41:25.060
can't compare.

41:26.130 --> 41:27.130
That's true.

41:27.930 --> 41:29.530
Let's try a peach blossom color
on your makeup.

41:29.570 --> 41:30.100
Hmm.

41:34.730 --> 41:35.410
Where are her bridal shoes?

41:37.980 --> 41:39.020
Don't tell me they were left in the car?

41:40.140 --> 41:41.060
The car is parked
at the village entrance.

41:41.340 --> 41:42.540
Never mind. I'll take you there.

41:42.540 --> 41:43.260
You might get lost.

41:43.380 --> 41:43.700
Okay.

41:48.220 --> 41:48.740
Qingyu.

41:48.980 --> 41:49.500
Could you

41:49.500 --> 41:50.380
straighten

41:50.380 --> 41:51.380
Xiaoyun's dress hem

41:51.540 --> 41:52.940
and help her put on this pendant?

41:53.220 --> 41:53.660
I'll leave it here.

42:30.650 --> 42:34.340
♪Perhaps♪

42:34.850 --> 42:40.550
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

42:41.690 --> 42:47.090
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

42:48.090 --> 42:53.650
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

42:59.320 --> 43:02.990
♪In the future♪

43:03.450 --> 43:09.170
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

43:10.670 --> 43:15.740
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

43:16.990 --> 43:22.150
♪That never expires♪

43:25.750 --> 43:30.220
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

43:31.220 --> 43:34.890
♪Is your name♪

43:35.390 --> 43:40.490
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

43:41.570 --> 43:44.790
♪At first sight♪

43:45.220 --> 43:48.500
♪The future has been determined♪

43:49.190 --> 43:54.750
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

43:55.850 --> 43:59.390
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

43:59.850 --> 44:03.790
♪Is a place♪

44:04.090 --> 44:09.650
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

44:10.320 --> 44:13.690
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

44:14.020 --> 44:17.490
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

44:18.020 --> 44:24.090
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
